{"tid":1908005,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部：中国從未發生宗教紛爭　宗教政策符合国情","createTime":"2020-03-03T03:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T04:31:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6c6a596a06184d95f47b0369c4eadb1546591ad6","tid":1908005,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"中國外交部人權事務特別代表劉華，在聯合國人權理事會發言，指中國從未發生過宗教紛爭，各類宗教在中國和諧共處，指這是中國傳統文化兼容、寬容精神的表現，也表明中國政府採取的宗教信仰政策符合國情。<br />\n<br />\n她說，中國憲法規定，任何國家機關、社會團體和個人不得強制公民信仰宗教或者不信仰宗教，不得歧視信教和不信教公民。中國的法例規定公民不分宗教信仰，平等享有選舉權、被選舉權、受教育權。婦女在法律上享有與男子一樣的平等權利，包括文化教育和宗教權利等。中方願與國際社會一道，促進婦女包括宗教信仰自由在內的各項權利。<br />\n<br />\n劉華表示，中國現有宗教團體5500多個，宗教院校近百所，宗教活動場所約14萬個。中國還有上百座清真寺專供女性穆斯林使用。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512161-20200303.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512161-20200303.htm&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpqe24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=8684706a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512161-20200303.htm&h=725918dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512161-20200303.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.epochweekly.com/uploads/pictures/1863/content_548-78-01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochweekly.com%2Fuploads%2Fpictures%2F1863%2Fcontent_548-78-01.jpg&h=d3d542cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c3a2481d0f8f9e904ede01557f72a6c2ebefd31","tid":1908005,"uid":9542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:39:06.000Z","msg":"共產黨咪最大邪教，中晒張圖啲特徵"},{"pid":"5afad44dd1a6ead370d63050bf710bf5d8c72602","tid":1908005,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c3a2481d0f8f9e904ede01557f72a6c2ebefd31","tid":1908005,"uid":9542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:39:06.000Z","msg":"共產黨咪最大邪教，中晒張圖啲特徵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime